title: NAACP Image Awards: The Rock, Taraji P. Henson, Tracee Ellis Ross & More (PHOTOS)
text:
Advertisement 
The Grammys weren’t the only star-studded Hollywood affair to take place this weekend! 
The NAACP Image Awards went down Saturday night and brought out the biggest names in television and film, including Taraji P. Henson, Trevor Noah and Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson, who was honored as “Entertainer of the Year” by the organization. 
Check out flicks from the NAACP Image Awards above.
